187
00:12:44,179 --> 00:12:44,739
Huân Nhi.

188
00:12:48,260 --> 00:12:48,900
Huân Nhi.

189
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:54,659
Tiêu Viêm ca ca.

190
00:12:56,060 --> 00:12:56,500
Huân Nhi.

191
00:12:57,460 --> 00:12:58,340
Huân Nhi, muội ở đâu?

192
00:13:23,099 --> 00:13:23,900
Tiêu Viêm ca ca.

193
00:13:24,820 --> 00:13:26,060
